   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Of the granary of the part of Ptolemais, of the crop of the 3rd indiction, Serenus, son of Harpalos, has shifted, through(?) Horkon(?), through Arios the donkey-driver, four donkeys, equal 4 donkeys. Mecheir 6.</ab>
